{"tid":1579441,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[倒數十日] 929全球反共運動！","createTime":"2019-09-18T14:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T18:16:36.000Z","uid":125861,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea2f8aaaa1fca76962630ad24eb44a2680c15aa","tid":1579441,"uid":125861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:42:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔該！大家！<br />\n<br />\n要做就推到全球各地響應！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mp84nJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmp84nJg.jpg&h=00475bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[請廣傳以下訊息]</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Dear people around the World,<br />\n<br />\nWe urge you to take notice of the rising threat of the China Communist Party. It isn&rsquo;t just an economic one, but also a threat to freedom, human rights and democracy of the entire free world.<br />\n<br />\nPlease #StandwithHK and join us in #929GlobalAntiChinaziMarch! <br />\n<br />\nSee you on 29/9! <br />\n<br />\nHongkongers </strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">What is ChiNazi?</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fUDPyOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfUDPyOR.jpg&h=62ab33b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThis is how Chinazi do business &amp; grow economy: <br />\n1. Theft of Intellectual Property<br />\n2. Trademark Infringement<br />\n3. Economic Invasions<br />\n4. Economic Suppression<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4WfKnHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4WfKnHg.jpg&h=d1712563&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jzFZbAB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt